[[Taggayt:Tutlayt taserɣint]]
'''Taɛṛabt tamɣribiyt''' nɣ '''Ddarija''' (s uskkil aɛṛab: الدّارجة) tga yat tantala taɛṛabt ittyusawaln ɣ [[lmɣrib]], aya a f illa umyarmas ar yat tskʷflt gr-as d [[Taɛṛabt tadzayrit|tɛṛabt tadzayrit]] d [[Taɛṛabt tatunsiyt|tɛṛabt tatunsiyt]] ar yat tskʷflt ikrin f tmzwarut. Tusi-d tantala-ad kigan zɣ ummzday-nns d [[tutlayin timaziɣin]], [[Tutlayt Talatint|talatint]] d [[Tutlayt tabuniqt|tbuniqt]] d [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfṛansist]] d [[Tutlayt Taṣbnyulit|tsbnyult]]. Imzarayn gr-as d tantlayin n ugmuḍ anammas mqqurn aylliɣ tt akkʷ ssiḍnn kra n imsnilsn, ɣ tsga n tntlayin ann yaḍn n tfriqt n ugafa, am tutlayt waḥdu-tt.

Taɛṛabt tamɣribiyt teṭṭaf mnnawt tmzarayin tinmnaḍin d iɣdbba (accents). Tamazrayt akkʷ ikkan f tiyyaḍ tga tt tin tgmmi tumlilt, Ṛṛbaṭ d Fas, aya nn a f tumẓ adɣar imqqurn ɣ usnɣms s unmgal n tmzarayin zun d tin [[Ṭanja]] d [[Wujda]].

